# --- Frontend (Vite) ---
# Written automatically by `npx convex dev`. Do not edit by hand.
# VITE_CONVEX_URL=https://<your-deployment>.convex.cloud

# --- Convex backend environment variables ---
# These are NOT read from this file. Set them in the Convex dashboard:
#   Settings → Environment Variables
# (or: npx convex env set NAME value)
#
#   GEMINI_API_KEY        (required) Google AI Studio key — "plan" mode + fallback
#   GROQ_API_KEY          (optional) Groq key — fast "ask" mode; falls back to Gemini
#   VOYAGE_API_KEY        (required) Voyage AI key — code embeddings (voyage-code-3)
#   GITHUB_WEBHOOK_SECRET (optional) shared secret for the push webhook (recommended)
#   GITHUB_TOKEN          (optional) raises GitHub rate limit 60 → 5000 req/h
#
# Optional model overrides:
#   GEMINI_MODEL          default: gemini-2.5-flash
#   GROQ_MODEL            default: llama-3.3-70b-versatile
#   EMBEDDING_MODEL       default: voyage-code-3
